    "product_description": "INKERASTORY - Ink Your Pet Story on Canvas\n\nTurn your favorite dog, cat, or pet photo into warm personalized wall art made for everyday home decor, thoughtful gifting, and meaningful keepsakes.\n\nEach piece is made to order from your uploaded pet photo. Add your pet's name, a short quote, a special date, or keep the design clean and portrait-focused. The result is a custom print that celebrates the pet who makes your home feel like home.\n\nPerfect for:\n- Dog portraits\n- Cat portraits\n- Pet memorial keepsakes\n- New pet parent gifts\n- Birthday and holiday gifts\n- Apartment, bedroom, office, or living room decor\n- Multi-pet family photos\n\nProduct Features:\n- Personalized design made from your pet photo\n- Premium HD printing\n- Fade-resistant inks\n- Available as Poster / Print Only or Stretched Canvas\n- Multiple sizes available\n- Warm, gift-ready pet portrait style\n- Ready-to-display canvas option\n\nHow It Works:\n1. Upload a clear pet photo after ordering\n2. Add optional name, quote, date, or note\n3. Choose print-only or stretched canvas\n4. We create your custom pet portrait artwork\n5. Receive a unique piece that keeps your pet's story close\n\nPhoto tip: bright, clear front-facing photos work best. For best results, avoid blurry screenshots, dark photos, or heavily filtered images.\n\nINKERASTORY - Because every pet story deserves a place on your wall.",
